      "title": "An n-populations model for traffic flow",
      "abstract": "A new and distinct cultivar of geranium named Fisrain, particularly characterized by the combined features of single flower form, light violet flower color, purple veins on upper petals, intense green leaves with strong zonation, vigorous growth habit and good branching ability, and medium to late flower response."
    },
    "121863306": {
      "title": "Measure valued solutions to conservation laws motivated by traffic modelling",
      "abstract": "Motivated by a traffic model, we study a conservation law whose solutions naturally need to be bounded Radon measures. We investigate the relations between this equation and finite systems of conservation laws that converge to it."
